cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CC

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on part-of-speech tagging. The use of a neural network (LSTM) also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The analysis of temporal structure and embeddings could also place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the comparison to a feedforward baseline suggests that it could belong to cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
